# AI Instructions for whatsmod

## Automatic Commit and Push
You MUST automatically commit and push your changes after completing every feature or task.
Use the provided automation script:
```bash
bash scripts/auto_commit_push.sh "Commit message"
```

Alternatively, follow the `/complete-feature` workflow defined in `.agent/workflows/complete-feature.md`.

## Workflow
1. Complete the coding task.
2. Verify the changes.
3. Run the auto-commit script with a descriptive message.
